<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Patch>
	
		<Operation Class="PatchOperationSequence">
			<success>Normal</success>
			<operations>
				
			<li Class="PatchOperationAdd">
				<xpath>/Defs/XmlExtensions.SettingsMenuDef[defName = "FrozenSnowFoxTweaksSettings"]/settings/li[tag="FrozenSnowFoxTweaksLTSAmmunitionSimple"]/settings</xpath>
				<value>

			
						
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.Text">
				<text>[LTS] Ammunition - Simple Ammo Pack Tweaks</text>
				<font>Medium</font>
				<anchor>Middle</anchor>
				<tKey>FSFTweaksLTSAmmunitionSimpleTweaksTitle</tKey>
			</li>
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.GapLine">
			</li>
			
			<!-- LTS Expensive Ammo -->
			
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.Checkbox">
				<label>Expensive Ammo</label>
				<key>FSFLTSExpensiveAmmo</key>
				<defaultValue>false</defaultValue>
				<tKey>FSFTweaksLTSExpensiveAmmoTitle</tKey>
			</li>
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.SetColor">
				<color>(163,177,188)</color>
			</li>
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.Text">
				<text>Changes the ammo crafting recipes from LTS to make ammunition more expensive to create.  The values are balanced around the idea that each ingredient will yield 1.5 units of ammo and each recipe will create 60 units of ammo.  The market price is automatically calculated based on the material costs.  Spacer ammo is made with a 1:2 ratio to make it somewhat cheaper than Ultratech ammo.</text>
				<tKey>FSFTweaksLTSExpensiveAmmoDesc</tKey>
			</li>
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.SetColor"/>
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.GapLine">
				<spacing>12</spacing>
			</li>
					
			<!-- LTS No Kit Movement Speed Malus -->
			
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.Checkbox">
				<label>No Kit Movement Speed Malus</label>
				<key>FSFLTSKitSpeedMalus</key>
				<defaultValue>false</defaultValue>
				<tKey>FSFTweaksLTSKitSpeedMalusTitle</tKey>
			</li>
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.SetColor">
				<color>(163,177,188)</color>
			</li>
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.Text">
				<text>Removes the movement speed malus from LTS Ammo Kits.</text>
				<tKey>FSFTweaksLTSKitSpeedMalusDesc</tKey>
			</li>
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.SetColor"/>
			
			<li Class="XmlExtensions.Setting.GapLine">
			</li>					
						
				
					
				</value>
			</li>
				
			</operations>
		</Operation>
	
</Patch>